quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,38,"Njookku-mi diina baabiraa…ďe am …ďen: Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba. Haananaa men nde men kafidata e Alla hay e huunde. ∆äuum ko jeyaa…óum e …ďural Alla e dow amen e hoore yim…ďe …ďeen; kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe njettataa."
  12,39,"Eehey mon won¬īdii…ďe am …ói…óo ka kaso! E ko dewetee…ói ceertu…ói …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, kaa ko Alla Gooto pool…óo o?"
  12,40,"On ndewani gah mum, si wonah in…óe …óe innu…óon …óum, onon e baabiraa…ďe mon, Alla jippinanaani …óen hujja. √Ďaawoore ndeen alanah si wanaa Alla. O yamirii wota on ndw si wanaa KaŇčko. Ko …óuum woni diina √Īii…ďuka kan; kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe nganndaa."
  12,41,"Eehey mon won¬īdii…ďe am …ói…óo ka kaso! Go…ó…óo e mo'on yarnay koohoo mun on sanngara; oya on, o fetee, colli …óin √Īaama ka hoore makko. Fiyaaku mo la…ďndi…óon fii mun on √Īaawaama."
  12,42,"O maakani on mo o sikke da…óay e ma…ď…ďe kam…ďe …ói…óo: "JaŇčto lam ka koohoojo maa on". Seytaane yejjintini mo jaŇčtanagol koohoojo makko on. [Yuusufu] √Īii…ďiti ka kaso yoga e duu…ďi."
  12,43,"Laam…óo on wi'i: "Min mi yi'ii (e koy…óol) na'i jee…ói…ói pay…ói, na √Īaama poo∆īu…ói jee…ói…ói …óin, e butaali jee…ói…ói kecci, e go…ó…ói goo joor…ói. Eheymon dental, pirtanee kam ngol koy…óol am, si on laatike firtoo…ďe koy…ói"."